CodeChef UPES Campus Chapter
June 5
UPES - ACM Student Chapter
June 4

#ChallengesWorldWide
UPES ACM and ACM-W has taken an initiative to keep all the aspiring coders and programmers well-acquainted with all the upcoming tech event...s that would bring out the coder in you. So buckle up coders, and keep hustlin'.

CodeChef presents to you "THE JUNE-LONG CHALLENGE", a 10-day monthly challenge created for all the aspiring coders out there. The competition provides you a platform to apply previously learned concepts, discover new ways to solve a problem and produce authentic and novel solutions. It is a great way to bring out the best in you as it pushes you to be better than others, and it's also a great utilisation of your summer break.
The June-Long Challenge is open to everyone across the globe.
For further information, please refer to the link below:
https://www.codechef.com/JUNE19
